    "description_long": "This bus shelter features a curved, transparent blue roof supported by four sturdy metallic columns. The shelter includes a wooden slat bench with a metal frame, providing seating for waiting passengers. On one side, there is a rectangular metal trash bin, enhancing the utility of the shelter. The back of the shelter is partially enclosed with a solid metallic panel, offering some protection from wind and rain. The overall design is modern and functional, with open sides for easy access. The materials and structure suggest durability and suitability for urban environments.",
